Class Tile.GrassTile

  • java.lang.Object

    Tile

    public static class Tile.GrassTile
extends Tile
    A class for grass. Grass cannot collapse and gives a Item.MudItem when broken. Grass can fall and appears at the very top of the ground.
    Author:
    Spencer Yoder
